{"tid":2022814,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[韓國電影]華麗的假期 - 5．18 光州事件40周年","createTime":"2020-05-18T14:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T15:05:50.000Z","uid":29751,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c8e77156ab94c562f73cee2a3a1bca9e4b9514b","tid":2022814,"uid":29751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KLeq0P0ow1Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKLeq0P0ow1Y&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=51db92f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KLeq0P0ow1Y</a><br />\n1979年韓國獨裁者朴正熙被韓國中情部部長金載圭殺死，全國各地燃起示威要求民主化，陸軍少將全斗煥發起軍事政變奪權並推行戒嚴。民主化示威愈演愈烈，全斗煥派出韓國軍隊鎮壓，軍人被告知示威者受到北韓煽動，令他們以為暴力鎮壓示威乃正當行為。1980年5月18日中午，在光州全羅南道廳前韓國國歌奏起時，軍隊開槍射向示威群眾鎮壓。"},{"pid":"95790f55a7b719e6d14f1acf4a78a5fb53fd2644","tid":2022814,"uid":89030,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:05:50.000Z","msg":"最後好慘烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />女主只可以係架車用大聲公叫大家支持"}]}